languages.text: "Надо же, чернь, и так складно говорит! Это даже мило. Ну развлеки меня. Расскажи о себе и об этом месте, что ли".
"Would you believe it — well-spoken rabble! It is rather sweet in its own way. Go on, then, amuse me. Tell me about yourself and this place."
languages.original_text: "Надо же, чернь, и так складно говорит! Это даже мило. Ну развлеки меня. Расскажи о себе и об этом месте, что ли".

languages.text: “真让人吃惊，你们这些下等人说话居然说得这么顺！很好，接着说吧，让我开心开心。介绍一下你自己，还有这个地方的情况。”

languages.text: «Increíble: ¡plebe bienhablada! Es adorable, a su modo. Adelante, entreténgame: hábleme de los suyos y de este lugar».
languages.original_text: "Would you believe it — well-spoken rabble! It is rather sweet in its own way. Go on, then, amuse me. Tell me about yourself and this place."

traits.locale_text: «Increíble: ¡plebe bienhablada! Es adorable, a su modo. Adelante, entreténgame: hábleme de los suyos y de este lugar».

languages.text: 「信じるっていうのか、口の上手い愚民が！これはこれなりに旨味がある。やってみろよ。私を驚かせてみろ。お前自身とこの場所について話すんだ」
languages.original_text: "Would you believe it — well-spoken rabble! It is rather sweet in its own way. Go on, then, amuse me. Tell me about yourself and this place."

traits.locale_text: 「信じるっていうのか、口の上手い愚民が！これはこれなりに旨味がある。やってみろよ。私を驚かせてみろ。お前自身とこの場所について話すんだ」

languages.text: "Kaum zu glauben – kultiviertes Gesinden! Das ist irgendwie richtig süß. Also gut, amüsiert mich. Erzählt mir von Euch und diesem Ort."
languages.original_text: "Would you believe it — well-spoken rabble! It is rather sweet in its own way. Go on, then, amuse me. Tell me about yourself and this place."

traits.locale_text: "Kaum zu glauben – kultiviertes Gesinden! Das ist irgendwie richtig süß. Also gut, amüsiert mich. Erzählt mir von Euch und diesem Ort."

languages.text: « Voyez-vous ça... La populace peut être bien élevée ! Comme c'est charmant. Très bien, divertissez-moi. Parlez-moi de vous et de cet endroit. »
languages.original_text: "Would you believe it — well-spoken rabble! It is rather sweet in its own way. Go on, then, amuse me. Tell me about yourself and this place."

languages.text: "Ayaktakımından hoşsohbet birisini gördüm ya, bir yaşıma daha girdim! Çok şirin bir durum aslında. İyi bakalım, eğle beni. Bana kendinden ve bu koloniden bahset."
languages.original_text: "Would you believe it — well-spoken rabble! It is rather sweet in its own way. Go on, then, amuse me. Tell me about yourself and this place."
